title: Happy Solsthelion Everyone
text:
The Solstice was December 21st, Perihelion is January 4th, and between them they neatly cover the usual holiday period.

So here's wishing everyone a Happy Solsthelion !!

title: Ask HN: Anyone Interested in Being a Mentor?
text:
Merry Christmas HN! Been a long time lurker and HN is one of the reasons I changed careers to tech at a not so young age :)

I’m still pretty new to tech but I would love to connect and learn from someone in the industry who’s willing to mentor me on how to navigate this path. I’m a data engineer. This could just mean a call every couple of months and be patient with me asking questions:)

Thanks for reading and Merry Christmas!
